data.Name: Tash Sultana
data.Bio: Natasha "Tash" Sultana (born 15th June, 1995) is an Australian singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist. Described as a "one-person band who brings new meaning to the concept of multi-tasking", they are best known for their 2016 single "Jungle", which was voted into third place in the Triple J Hottest 100, 2016. Sultana initially made a name for themself busking on the streets of Melbourne and having homemade videos go viral getting millions of views online. Read more on Last.fm
